{"tid":2358640,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"為大麻合法化開路－聯合國經投票結果正式承認「醫療用大麻」","createTime":"2021-01-08T09:32:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T07:22:43.000Z","uid":58335,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d96ed504cca5f3a85282872aaa7c0509fc5ed339","tid":2358640,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:32:59.000Z","msg":"連登仔:聯合國係道友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聯合國（UN）麻醉藥品委員會（Commission for Narcotic Drugs）於本週正式投票是否將大麻及大麻相關物質從《1961年麻醉品單一公約》的附表四中移除，最終結果為「通過」：27 票贊成、25 票反對、1 票棄權。此決定意味著大麻和大麻相關物質的管制等級將會降低，其中受到管制的麻醉品包括海洛因等最危險的成癮性物質。<br />\n<br />\n近年不少國家紛紛宣布承認醫療用大麻，本次投票則是遵從世界衞生組織（WHO）於 2019 年 1 月的建議，希望改變大麻和大麻相關物質的管制範圍，如今官方正式承認醫療用大麻，不過於非醫療用途時仍是禁止非法。外界認為此重大改變將為醫療用大麻開路，因為許多國家是以聯合國公約為立法標準，如今確定放寬即可修例推動醫療用大麻之合法化，以後再為休閒合法大麻鋪路，對於種種有關大麻的政策有著深遠的影響。<br />\n<br />\n據了解投下同意票國家包括美國與許多歐洲國家，<span class=\"red\">反對票國家包括中國、俄羅斯，巴基斯坦與埃及等國。</span><br />\n<br />\n資料來源:Un<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2020/12/cannabis-officially-medicine-un-vote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2020%2F12%2Fcannabis-officially-medicine-un-vote&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIR1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=4dabe9ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2020/12/cannabis-officially-medicine-un-vote</a>"},{"pid":"5063047d0bff32c44714ca0a033222a5f508f6c5","tid":2358640,"uid":79793,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:43:02.000Z","msg":"連登守舊撚 雙重標準<br />\n<br />\n飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc048d291e74ffcb096f965777f4b7d9437421d","tid":2358640,"uid":7482,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:45:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩話 醫療用大麻合法化 <br />\n前排先有個政府既出黎UP話香港絕對唔會大麻合法化 <br />\n又唔跟聯合國阿 平時好鍾意拎出黎鞭人屍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918a2ecd98e2cc9637fd807e757caa36392f50e6","tid":2358640,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0bc048d291e74ffcb096f965777f4b7d9437421d","tid":2358640,"uid":7482,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:45:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩話 醫療用大麻合法化 <br />\n前排先有個政府既出黎UP話香港絕對唔會大麻合法化 <br />\n又唔跟聯合國阿 平時好鍾意拎出黎鞭人屍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:54:38.000Z","msg":"你講緊果個逃犯天堂？"},{"pid":"95e0fe9100c2ffbdede65fa39974cdf91b116a80","tid":2358640,"uid":258899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:55:30.000Z","msg":"聯合國道友 ！！！"},{"pid":"bde0dbbc60681c0702ee2f8537035b370b0f90ca","tid":2358640,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T10:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08466655af0c0f43d95760a78dc856eeef2f01ca","tid":2358640,"uid":137480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5063047d0bff32c44714ca0a033222a5f508f6c5","tid":2358640,"uid":79793,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:43:02.000Z","msg":"連登守舊撚 雙重標準<br />\n<br />\n飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T10:01:37.000Z","msg":"雙重你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成世人都唔食煙飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b34fa94b9847fe93297952b282d6a38217bf4bd","tid":2358640,"uid":197121,"like":0,"